    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a href=&quot;https://jazz.net/learn/LearnItem.jsp?href=content/docs/work-items/index.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>Getting&#xD;
