&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>&#xD;
    See the &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../../core.default.tool_def.extend-ibm/tools/rtc_407F3232.html&quot;&#xD;
